{"tid":675191,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港交通真係好唔掂","createTime":"2018-05-23T10:29:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T11:03:12.000Z","uid":72703,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"04248b09a6c87755ef358054319fed8b5d409d7a","tid":675191,"uid":72703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T10:29:33.000Z","msg":"難得可以準時放工<br />\n<br />\n繁忙時間地鐵完全超出100%載客量<br />\n大站迫幾班車都上唔到<br />\n<br />\n巴士實時系統永世都唔準確<br />\n成日都走車 或者miss咗成架無嚟<br />\n上到巴士成架滿哂，啲廢老唔肯行入啲，<br />\n仲要一邊嘈點解唔整多幾個關愛座，<br />\n轉個頭有人讓座，佢地為咗個位打哂交咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港好多私家車啲司機都唔肯好好地排隊<br />\n係都要係外線cut入嚟爭過燈位<br />\n大佬呀，咁樣要讓嚟讓去仲浪費時間，<br />\n每次燈位淨係過到幾架車，足足等咗六次燈先上到橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到底香港仲有咩交通工具可以搭？<br />\n定係以後都唔好揀準時放工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"239076abf95e944910faf59c2f9a2040607f6a96","tid":675191,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T10:39:19.000Z","msg":"電單車幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3dddbed12c7e781b6a96ebc624c222ceb782409","tid":675191,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T10:41:05.000Z","msg":"的士狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fbcabc71d2fddd01a3bc5a49ff8890f1813eee5","tid":675191,"uid":156751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T11:03:12.000Z","msg":"行路返工不是夢 要過海帶埋泳褲"}]}